                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The animated silverware swarm attempts to pin a single creature.</p>\n<p>The target must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"17\" data-pf2-label=\"Stick a Fork in It DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Silverware pins portions of the target's clothing and gear. The target takes a -10-foot circumstance penalty to its Speeds as long as it remains in the swarm's space.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, and the target also can't Step until it leaves the swarm's space.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is thoroughly pinned by the silverware, becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized} until it Escapes (DC 17) or uses 2 Interact actions to remove all of the silverware pinning them down.</p>"
